<figureCitation box="[1125,1214,1843,1869]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,582,606]" captionTargetBox="[155,1432,192,549]" captionTargetId="figure-20@5.[148,1440,181,558]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Male genitalia, ventral and lateral view. A) C. hintoni. B) C. costae. C). C. milleri." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6405138" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6405138/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="232">Fig. 3C</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
